Privacy Policy
Pocket Games Entertainment Sp. z o.o.
("we," "our," or "us") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile games.
1. Information We Collect
We do not directly collect personal information. However, we may collect the following types of non-personal information:
Device Information
: Information about the device you use to access our games, such as the device model, operating system, and unique device identifiers.
Usage Information
: Information about your interactions with our games, including gameplay data, preferences, and in-game purchases.
Ad Networks
: We use third-party ad networks like AdMob, UnityAds, and Chartboost. These networks may collect and use your data to show personalized ads based on your interests.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information to:
Provide and improve our games.
Process in-game purchases.
Show relevant advertisements.
Analyze gameplay data to enhance user experience.
Ensure compliance with legal obligations.
3. Third-Party Services
Our games incorporate third-party services:
AdMob, UnityAds, and Chartboost
: These ad networks collect and use your data to deliver personalized ads. They have their own privacy policies that detail their data collection and use practices.
Payment Processors
: For in-game purchases, we use third-party payment processors who collect and process payment information. They have their own privacy policies.
4. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.
5. Your Choices
Ad Preferences
: You can opt-out of personalized ads through your device settings.
Access and Deletion
: If you wish to access or delete your personal information, please contact us at Pocket.Games.Entertainment.Sup@gmail.com. We will respond to your request in accordance with applicable laws.
6. Children's Privacy
Our games are not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected such information, please contact us at Pocket.Games.Entertainment.Sup@gmail.com so we can delete it.
7. Limitation of Liability
We do not take any responsibility for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or revenues, whether incurred directly or indirectly, or any loss of data, use, goodwill, or other intangible losses, resulting from:
Your access to or use of or inability to access or use our games;
Any conduct or content of any third party on our games;
Any content obtained from our games; and
Unauthorized access, use, or alteration of your transmissions or content.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Pocket Games Entertainment Sp. z o.o.
Email:
Pocket.Games.Entertainment.Sup@gmail.com
Thank you for playing our games and trusting us with your information!